NOTE Language: en

00:00:09.634 --> 00:00:11.760
If you cannot enjoy in Sahaja Yoga,

00:00:11.885 --> 00:00:14.419
then you should know that something is wrong with you.

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:18.013
If you cannot feel happy in Sahaja Yoga, then you must know

00:00:18.139 --> 00:00:20.722
that there’s something definitely wrong with you.

00:00:20.842 --> 00:00:23.759
If you cannot enjoy the company of sahaja yogis,

00:00:23.842 --> 00:00:27.137
then be sure something is wrong with you.

00:00:27.218 --> 00:00:33.593
If you cannot laugh and appreciate the greatness of God,

00:00:33.718 --> 00:00:36.359
then something wrong with you.

00:00:36.505 --> 00:00:40.172
If you are still worried about negative people and their problems

00:00:40.297 --> 00:00:43.588
then know that there’s something wrong with you.

00:00:43.907 --> 00:00:46.324
If you have sympathies with negative people,

00:00:46.449 --> 00:00:49.324
then also there’s something wrong with you.

00:00:49.447 --> 00:00:54.031
But if you have anger for negative and all that is negative

00:00:54.155 --> 00:01:00.342
that is against Sahaja Yoga, then you are there.

00:01:05.394 --> 00:01:10.764
If you know how to get fun out of the so-called

00:01:10.845 --> 00:01:13.743
discomforts, then you should know

00:01:13.850 --> 00:01:16.339
you are on the right lights.

00:01:16.405 --> 00:01:21.447
And as you start becoming discreet automatically,

00:01:21.528 --> 00:01:24.861
you should know you are progressing well.

00:01:25.027 --> 00:01:28.178
As you become more peaceful and your temper

00:01:28.277 --> 00:01:32.610
vanishes in the thin air as soon as you see somebody

00:01:32.691 --> 00:01:38.370
attacking you, then know that you are progressing well.

00:01:38.623 --> 00:01:46.236
As soon as you see a ordeal or a calamity falling on

00:01:46.317 --> 00:01:52.330
the personality and you do not get worried about it,

00:01:52.411 --> 00:01:55.478
then know that you are progressing.

00:01:55.569 --> 00:02:01.986
When no amount of artificiality can impress you,

00:02:02.111 --> 00:02:05.175
then know that you are progressing.

00:02:05.256 --> 00:02:14.090
No amount of material well-being in others

00:02:14.175 --> 00:02:19.050
makes you unhappy, no more unhappy,

00:02:19.175 --> 00:02:23.041
then know that you are progressing well.

00:02:23.108 --> 00:02:27.899
No amount of

00:02:33.565 --> 00:02:36.732
labor or

00:02:37.857 --> 00:02:48.899
or troubles are sufficient to become a Sahaja yogi.

00:02:49.066 --> 00:02:53.441
Any – whatever you may try, one cannot become a Sahaja yogi,

00:02:53.559 --> 00:02:59.503
while you have got it without any effort.

00:02:59.688 --> 00:03:03.456
So you are something special.

00:03:03.556 --> 00:03:07.473
So this, once you understand that you are special,

00:03:07.639 --> 00:03:11.342
you will become humble about it.

00:03:11.342 --> 00:03:17.136
Then when it happens to you that you’ve humbled down

00:03:17.217 --> 00:03:19.842
when you see you have achieved something,

00:03:20.008 --> 00:03:22.092
that you have some powers,

00:03:22.259 --> 00:03:28.008
that you are emitting innocence, that you are discreet,

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:32.717
and as a result of that you become more compassion,

00:03:32.883 --> 00:03:36.967
humbler personality, a sweeter personality,

00:03:37.134 --> 00:03:40.342
then you should believe

00:03:40.508 --> 00:03:44.592
that you are in the heart of your Mother.

00:03:44.725 --> 00:03:48.491
This is what is the sign of the new Sahaja yogi now

00:03:48.491 --> 00:03:57.051
in the new era, who has to move with new force.

00:03:58.411 --> 00:04:04.617
Where you will grow so fast that without meditation,

00:04:04.728 --> 00:04:07.691
you will be in meditation;

00:04:08.605 --> 00:04:13.786
without being in My presence, you will be in My presence;

00:04:14.266 --> 00:04:22.053
without asking, you will be blessed by your Father.

00:04:22.306 --> 00:04:25.264
This is what you are in for;

00:04:25.364 --> 00:04:31.406
and again I welcome you to this new era today,

00:04:31.540 --> 00:04:34.975
on this great day of Sahasrara.

00:04:35.061 --> 00:04:38.016
May God bless you all.
